title: I AM ATHLETE | Season 3 Recap: The Evolution Continues
description:
SUBSCRIBE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE?sub_confirmation=1

In Episode 53 of I Am Athlete, Brandon Marshall, Adam "Pacman" Jones, LeSean "Shady" McCoy, and Omar Kelly come together to address all of the changes that took place in season 3, while recapping some of the season’s better discussions and interviews.
